00:45:38,620 --> 00:45:39,660
I’m fine.

849
00:45:40,570 --> 00:45:41,810
What are you doing?

850
00:45:42,770 --> 00:45:44,620
Believe it or not? There’s a bug.

851
00:45:46,050 --> 00:45:47,140
Make way. Make way.

852
00:45:47,140 --> 00:45:47,920
Disgusting.

853
00:45:51,490 --> 00:45:52,230
You stepped on my foot!

854
00:45:57,620 --> 00:45:58,230
Sir.

855
00:45:59,010 --> 00:46:00,700
How much time did I use?

856
00:46:02,620 --> 00:46:04,250
Less than fifteen minutes.

857
00:46:04,250 --> 00:46:06,490
Much faster than last time.

858
00:46:09,770 --> 00:46:12,730
The formation of your school
is wonderful.

859
00:46:12,730 --> 00:46:15,180
The more I think about it,
the more interesting I feel.

860
00:46:16,570 --> 00:46:17,940
It took me a long time

861
00:46:17,940 --> 00:46:19,280
to understand it.

862
00:46:20,770 --> 00:46:22,710
You’re a clever man.

863
00:46:23,460 --> 00:46:24,380
You’ve learnt all our formations

864
00:46:24,380 --> 00:46:26,620
when you learn for the first time.

865
00:46:27,180 --> 00:46:30,300
It proves I have a good taste.

866
00:46:31,380 --> 00:46:33,630
You’re a young talent
from the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

867
00:46:34,050 --> 00:46:37,420
I can’t take you as my disciple.

868
00:46:38,220 --> 00:46:41,050
But I want our formations

869
00:46:41,050 --> 00:46:43,800
and martial art books to be inherited

870
00:46:44,900 --> 00:46:48,720
instead of vanishing with me.

871
00:46:49,730 --> 00:46:51,220
What have I done

872
00:46:51,220 --> 00:46:53,250
to deserve your gracious kindness?

873
00:47:00,110 --> 00:47:03,620
♪Stars flow like river♪

874
00:47:04,680 --> 00:47:08,280
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

875
00:47:08,850 --> 00:47:12,920
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

876
00:47:13,170 --> 00:47:16,810
♪I will never be alone♪

877
00:47:16,810 --> 00:47:20,930
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

878
00:47:21,350 --> 00:47:25,780
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

879
00:47:26,440 --> 00:47:31,000
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

880
00:47:31,230 --> 00:47:35,860
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

881
00:47:36,050 --> 00:47:39,880
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

882
00:47:40,100 --> 00:47:44,790
♪When I go across the world for you♪

883
00:47:45,050 --> 00:47:48,790
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

884
00:47:49,120 --> 00:47:54,210
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

885
00:47:54,210 --> 00:47:58,150
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

886
00:47:58,150 --> 00:48:02,680
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

887
00:48:03,300 --> 00:48:10,400
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

888
00:48:11,140 --> 00:48:15,770
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

